    A timeseries entry in a ordered structure with accessors for the previous and next items in the time series.
    This is where the component calculations for the GrowthRate method are performed. The calculations for the cori method are not performed until the recache() method is called, which is done by the GrowthRateEstimator::estimateForProfile method when considering a new infectivity profile.
